headlines.description: — Corey Seager took a mighty swing and barely connected, sending a squibber through an open area on the left side of the infield for his team's first hit in the seventh inning.
headlines.shortLinkText: Texas Rangers win first World Series title with 5-0 victory over Arizona Diamondbacks in Game 5
